  "title": "Service Engineer (CCTV)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>MNC Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2500 - $3000 + Allowance + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: West</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: Monday to Friday (8.30am to 5.30pm)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attend to equipment fault at customers’ premises</li>\n  <li>Liaise with the customer and sub-contractors regarding all aspect on the add-on project activities</li>\n  <li>Monitor the progress of the work done closely in order to ensure that the schedule and quality of work are met</li>\n  <li>Ensure that all materials and equipment are delivered on time as per schedule for site installation or rectification of fault</li>\n  <li>To carry out periodic maintenance for our customers</li>\n  <li>Any others ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum Nitec and/or Diploma in Electronics and/or Electrical Engineering or relevant field with 1-2 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Possess Class 3 Driving License will be an advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
